This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-userapp-package layer.

This layer provides user application packages for embedded Linux systems built with Yocto Project.

Dependencies
============

  URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/poky
  branch: kirkstone

  URI: git://git.openembedded.org/meta-openembedded
  branch: kirkstone

  URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/meta-raspberrypi
  branch: kirkstone

Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-userapp-package layer to the project repository:
https://github.com/pavan-gidaveer_henrg/meta-userapp-package.git

Maintainer: Pavan Kumar <pavan.gidaveer@henrg.com>

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-userapp-package layer to your build
 II. Layer Contents
III. Building Applications


I. Adding the meta-userapp-package layer to your build
======================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-userapp-package'

II. Layer Contents
==================

This layer contains:
- User application recipes with LED control and HTTPS server functionality
- IoT Security Gateway implementation
- Sample applications and examples

III. Building Applications
==========================

To build the applications provided by this layer:
- bitbake blink
- bitbake iot-security-gateway (when available)
- bitbake user-application (when available)
